PrecisOrder fixing (a) WEDNESDAY, DECEMBER 1, 1999, as the day upon which section 104 of this Act [BILL C-25], being chapter 35 of the Statutes of Canada, 1998, shall COME INTO FORCE, as well as sections 106, 122, 123 and 125 with respect to the Military Police Complaints Commission, and (b) WEDNESDAY, MARCH 1, 2000, as the day upon which sections 106, 122, 123, and 125 of this Act shall COME INTO FORCE with respect to the Canadian Forces Grievance Board.

precis:
Order fixing (a) WEDNESDAY, DECEMBER 1, 1999, as the day upon which
section 104 of this Act [BILL C-25], being chapter 35 of the Statutes of
Canada, 1998, shall COME INTO FORCE, as well as sections 106, 122, 123 and
125 with respect to the Military Police Complaints Commission, and
(b) WEDNESDAY, MARCH 1, 2000, as the day upon which sections 106, 122, 123,
and 125 of this Act shall COME INTO FORCE with respect to the Canadian
Forces Grievance Board.
